sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_018_1_CSMS: Unlock Connector - With Charging Session (Not fixed cable)
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.6.3 | Table 137 | Page 122
    Note over CP,CS: Reusable State: Charging (Table 201, Page 174)

    CS->>CP: 1. UnlockConnector.req
    CP-->>CS: 2. UnlockConnector.conf

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    CP->>CS: 5. StopTransaction.req
    CS-->>CP: 6. StopTransaction.conf

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver unplugs the cable.]

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Tool Validations:
    Note over CP,CS: Step 2: UnlockConnector.conf → status is Unlocked
    Note over CP,CS: Step 3: StatusNotification.req → status is Finishing
    Note over CP,CS: Step 5: StopTransaction.req → reason is UnlockCommand
    Note over CP,CS: Step 7: StatusNotification.req → status is Available
